<div class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300 min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6">
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-gold">Welcome to CodePeer Review</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-center mb-8 text-gray-400">A platform for collaborating, sharing, and reviewing code with your peers.</p>
  
  <div class="max-w-md mx-auto bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <form id="landingForm" method="get">
      <input
        type="email"
        id="emailInput"
        name="email"
        placeholder="Enter your email"
        class="w-full px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700 text-gray-200 placeholder-gray-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:ring-teal-400"
        required
      />
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-200">Receive updates on new features and special offers from CodePeer Review.</p>
      <button type="submit" class="mt-4 bg-teal-600 text-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-teal-600/80 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 w-full">
        <span class="text-xl font-semibold">Sign Up</span>
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
  
  <p class="mt-8 text-center text-gray-400">Engage with others' code to learn and grow together!</p>
  <div class="mt-auto text-center text-gray-400">
    <p>Â© 2024 CodePeer Review. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#" class="hover:underline">Terms of Service</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 max-w-md mx-auto bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gold">About the Site</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-200">CodePeer Review is dedicated to helping developers collaborate and learn from each other. Join us and start improving your coding skills today.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 max-w-md mx-auto bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gold">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
    <div class="mb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-200">How can I start collaborating on CodePeer Review?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-100">Simply sign up with your email address and start exploring available projects to collaborate on.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-200">What are the benefits of using CodePeer Review?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-100">CodePeer Review provides detailed feedback on your code, allows you to learn from other developers, and helps you build meaningful connections in the community.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  document.getElementById("landingForm").addEventListener("submit", function(event) {
    event.preventDefault();  // Prevent the default form submission

    var email = document.getElementById("emailInput").value;

    window.location.href = "<%= new_user_registration_path %>?email=" + encodeURIComponent(email);
  });
</script>
